{
  "stem": "942.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that's the only thing we had as liquid, liquid, you know, because we were, we were completely dehydrated.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We arrived in a place, I think it was called [INAUDIBLE] or Breslau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't remember for sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were taken to this railroad yard, and we were put into open box cars, these metal cars-- the open ones that carries iron or coal, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we were stuffed in into these cars, and-- just like sardines.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And only the heads were sticking out, like a bunch of cabbages, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I think this helped to keep our bodies, at least, warm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But our heads were pretty cold, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There was nothing on our ears, you know, and-- and a train was going west.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We came into Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I remember the train stopped in a town called [INAUDIBLE] at a railway station, and it was early morning.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was a dirty, early morning snow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was still dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I guess it was probably around 7:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was a snow drizzle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there was a walkway over the rail where people walk across the railway yard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as soon as the Czech people saw-- or how they got wind of it, I don't know-- but a lot of Czech people came with these big bakers' breads.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they started to throw bread and buns into the train.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Unfortunately, in there, I was too far.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I couldn't catch anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the Nazis, you know, when we stopped at this station in [INAUDIBLE], they got off the train, and they were patrolling all around the train, so that nobody can run away from this train, you see.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they were yelling at the people not to throw bread, because these are Jews, you see.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
